text LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_InterviewRequest {
	"Oh, hello! You were in a POKéMON
	CONTEST, weren't you?
	It's easy to tell from your POKéMON.

	I'm a reporter. I'm working on a story
	on POKéMON CONTESTS.

	If I may, would you be willing to answer
	a few questions?"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_DescribeContest {
	"Oh, you will?
	Thank you.

	Briefly, how would you describe the
	CONTEST you just entered?"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_WhatImageWhenYouHearX {
	"Ah, I see.
	That's a very edifying comment.

	You get a good feel for what
	the CONTEST was like.

	I've got one last question.

	When you hear the word “{STR_VAR_2},”
	what image do you get?"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_ThatsAllForInterview {
	"I see!

	So that's how you imagine the concept
	of “{STR_VAR_2}” to be.

	Thank you!
	You've given me some good ideas.

	I think I can write a good story on
	POKéMON CONTESTS now.

	Maybe, just maybe, this story will even
	make it to television.
	I hope you'll look forward to it!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_PleaseDoShareStoryWithMe {
	"Oh, too bad…

	Well, if you come across a good story,
	please do share it with me."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_LookingForwardToNextContest {
	"I'll be looking forward to your next
	POKéMON CONTEST."
}

