}

text gTVNameRaterText03 {
	"A nickname fit for a unique individual
	of a POKéMON!

	If raised properly, this POKéMON's
	uniqueness will bloom excessively!"
}

text gTVNameRaterText04 {
	"A nickname that will nurture the caring
	and compassionate side of POKéMON.

	If raised properly, this POKéMON will
