	That POKéMON should remain fit and
	robust for a long, long time."
}

text gTVNameRaterText07 {
	"A good nickname that should make the
	POKéMON very active!

	I should think that this POKéMON will be
	a strong performer in battles."
}

text gTVNameRaterText08 {
	"An appealing nickname that should make
	the POKéMON very charming!

	I don't doubt that this POKéMON will be
	quite the charmer in POKéMON CONTESTS."
}

text gTVNameRaterText09 {
	"The nickname {STR_VAR_1} is rooted by
	the letter “{STR_VAR_3}.”

	That letter is supported by the first
	letter “{STR_VAR_2},” which gives it a solid sense
	of presence as a nickname."
}

text gTVNameRaterText10 {
	"The nickname {STR_VAR_1} is very
	shapely in a pleasing manner.

	The presence of the letters “{STR_VAR_2}” and
	“{STR_VAR_3}”--now that is remarkably good!"
}

text gTVNameRaterText11 {
	"The nickname {STR_VAR_1}--it has a
