	Tune in next time as we visit another
	SECRET BASE! Thanks for joining us!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_StoppedMoving1 {
	"The visitor has stopped!

	The visitor isn't moving at all!

	Was {STR_VAR_1}'s SECRET BASE
	that unimpressive?"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_StoppedMoving2 {
	"The visitor has stopped!

	The visitor isn't moving at all!

	Is it fatigue?
	Has the visitor grown weary?"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedChair {
	"The visitor sat down on a chair!
	The visitor is seated!

	Look at that look of delight!

	That chair must be very comfortable
	to get that response!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedBalloon {
	"The visitor charged at a balloon!

	It burst!
	Oh, my goodness, it popped!

	The visitor appears startled by
	the sudden noise!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedTent {
	"The visitor entered a TENT!

	The visitor is running around!

	Oh, my, the visitor is frolicking!

	The visitor appears surprised by
	the TENT's size!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedPlant {
	"The visitor is examining
	a potted plant!

	The visitor has surprisingly
	mature taste!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedGoldShield {
	"The visitor is examining
	a GOLD SHIELD!

	The visitor's eyes appear to be
	lit up with wonder!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedSilverShield {
	"The visitor is examining
	a SILVER SHIELD!

	The visitor appears to be wide-eyed!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedGlassOrnament {
	"The visitor is examining
	a GLASS ORNAMENT!

	Oh, no!

	The visitor is touching it!

	It's getting covered with
	fingerprints…"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedTV {
	"The visitor is watching television!

	Looks like we have a big fan of TV!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedMudBall {
	"The visitor stomped on a MUD BALL!

	The visitor looks delighted!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedBag {
	"…Oh?

	The visitor is reaching for their own
	BAG and rummaging about in it!

	The visitor pulled out
	one {STR_VAR_2}!

	Look at the visitor smile while
	holding up the {STR_VAR_2}!

	It's like a TV commercial!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedCushion {
	"The visitor grabs a cushion and…"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_HitCushion {
	"…begins hitting it!

	Is the visitor under a lot of stress?"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_HuggedCushion {
	"…hugs it tight!

	Could the visitor be feeling happy
	about something?"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_BattledWon {
	"The visitor is chatting with
	{STR_VAR_1}!

	It looks like they're going to
	have a battle!

	And…

	It's the visitor!
	The visitor won an away match!

	The visitor is doing
	a victory dance!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_BattledLost {
	"The visitor is chatting with
	{STR_VAR_1}!

	It looks like they're going to
	have a battle!

	And…

	It's {STR_VAR_1}!
	The visitor has lost!

	The visitor looks dejected!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_DeclinedBattle {
	"The visitor is chatting with
	{STR_VAR_1}!

	It looks like they're going to
	have a battle!

	And…

	No, the visitor has refused!

	There won't be a battle after all!

	Did the visitor find {STR_VAR_1}
	unappealing?"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedPoster {
	"The visitor is staring intently
	at a poster!

	Is the poster to the visitor's
	liking?

	…But… There's something disturbing
	about the visitor's stares."
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedNoteMat {
	"The visitor stepped on a NOTE MAT!

	…Hmm…
	The visitor composed a funny tune!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_BattledDraw {
	"The visitor is chatting with
	{STR_VAR_1}!

	It looks like they're going to
	have a battle!

	And…

	It's a draw!
	Nothing's resolved!

	Both TRAINERS appear to be very
	disappointed!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedSpinMat {
	"The visitor stepped on
	a SPIN MAT!

	It looks like the visitor is dizzy!

	The visitor is tottering about!
	Look out!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedSandOrnament {
	"The visitor is reaching for
	a SAND ORNAMENT!

	Oh!

	It crumbled!
	It's fallen apart!

	The visitor looks sheepish
	and guilty!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedDesk {
	"The visitor is rubbing a desktop
	with their finger!

	Apparently, the visitor disapproves
	of dust!

	The visitor is surprisingly concerned
	about neatness!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedBrick {
	"The visitor is staring at a BRICK!

	Perhaps the visitor is thinking about
	the object on the BRICK."
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedSolidBoard {
	"The visitor is walking across
	the SOLID BOARD.

	The visitor keeps looking down.

	The visitor appears to be surprisingly
	timid and cautious!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedFence {
	"The visitor is looking intently
	at a FENCE!

	Has a new idea for a trap popped
	into the visitor's head?"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedGlitterMat {
	"The visitor stepped on
	a GLITTER MAT!

	The visitor is striking a variety
	of poses!

	The visitor appears to be fantasizing
	about being an idol!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedTire {
	"The visitor is staring intently
	at a TIRE!

	Could the visitor be thinking about
	the kind of car that would use it?"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedStand {
	"The visitor climbed a STAND!

	The visitor is looking out across
	{STR_VAR_1}'s BASE from high up!

	And…

	Lets loose a roar!
	The visitor is roaring!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_BrokeDoor {
	"The visitor charged headlong into
	a BREAKABLE DOOR!

	The visitor is laughing uproariously!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedDoll {
	"The visitor is talking to a DOLL!

	…It's a little creepy…"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedSlide {
	"The visitor is climbing the ladder
	on a SLIDE!

	And…

	The visitor slid down!

	Looks like the visitor is having
	a grand old time!"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedSlideButDidntGoDown {
	"The visitor is climbing the ladder
	on a SLIDE!

	And…

	The visitor went back down
	the ladder!

	Did the visitor suddenly chicken out?"
}

text TVSecretBaseSecrets_Text_UsedJumpMat {
	"The visitor stepped on
	a JUMP MAT!

	The visitor jumped once!

	Jumped twice!

	And a successful landing!

	The visitor is clapping!
	What a solo performance!"
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText00 {
	"SAFARI FAN CLUB!

	REPORTER: All right, mates!
	Tossing them SAFARI BALLS, are you?

	You can bet I am here in the SAFARI
	ZONE chock-full of amazing POKéMON!

	Let's get with it and have a chat with
	this good fellow of a SAFARI GUIDE!

	All right, mate, how are the visiting
	TRAINERS looking?"
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText01 {
	"GUIDE: Everyone seems to be going
	hard at it.

	{STR_VAR_1} is doing especially well.

	Why, before, {STR_VAR_1} caught
	{STR_VAR_2} POKéMON."
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText02 {
	"The TRAINER is clever with {POKEBLOCK}S.
	Used {STR_VAR_2} that time, I think."
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText03 {
	"The TRAINER didn't use a single
	{POKEBLOCK}! Not a one!

	There's an expert for you."
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText04 {
	"REPORTER: Is that right, then?

	Sounds like our mate {STR_VAR_1}
	is a stout SAFARI master!

	GUIDE: I hope the TRAINER comes back
	and shows us that great technique."
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText05 {
	"GUIDE: No one seems to be doing
	very well.

	{STR_VAR_1} had it especially bad.

	Why, before, the TRAINER only
	managed to catch {STR_VAR_2} POKéMON."
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText06 {
	"GUIDE: No one seems to be doing
	very well.

	{STR_VAR_1} had it especially bad.

	Why, before, the TRAINER didn't
	catch one POKéMON. Not a one!"
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText07 {
	"The TRAINER does use {POKEBLOCK}S.
	Used {STR_VAR_2} that time, I think.

	But, boy, I wish the TRAINER would
	get a bit better at this."
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText08 {
	"I think the TRAINER would have better
	luck using {POKEBLOCK}S, which weren't
	used at all that time."
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText09 {
	"REPORTER: Is that right, then?

	Sounds like our mate {STR_VAR_1}
	needs more SAFARI seasoning.

	GUIDE: I hope the TRAINER visits
	over and over to get the hang of it."
}

text gTVSafariFanClubText10 {
	"REPORTER: Quite right, it is!
	Facing up to challenges is important!

	Viewers, come on down to the SAFARI
	and make the challenge yourself!

	Until next time, cheerio!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_Intro {
	"“POKéMON CONTEST LIVE UPDATES!”

	MC: Thanks for joining us!

	We're live from the just-ended
	{STR_VAR_1} site.

	The hall is still filled with
	an audience unwilling to leave.

	Spectator: {STR_VAR_2}!

	Spectator: {STR_VAR_3}!

	MC: As you've just heard, the CONTEST
	was won by the POKéMON {STR_VAR_2}
	of {STR_VAR_3}.

	Spectator: {STR_VAR_2}!
	You're the best!

	Spectator: {STR_VAR_3}!
	Way to go!

	MC: Let's hear what the fans have
	to say about this CONTEST."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_WonBothRounds {
	"Spectator: The {STR_VAR_2} was tops in
	both primary and secondary judging!

	That {STR_VAR_2} will keep winning!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_BetterRound2 {
	"Spectator: The {STR_VAR_2} didn't do
	well in the primary judging, but it
	cleaned up in the secondary judging!

	It was a miraculous comeback
	for that {STR_VAR_2}. Yippee!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_EqualRounds {
	"Spectator: The {STR_VAR_2} remained
	consistent throughout both primary
	and secondary judging.

	{STR_VAR_3} and the {STR_VAR_2},
	they're no ordinary combo!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_BetterRound1 {
	"Spectator: In terms of being {STR_VAR_1},
	that {STR_VAR_2} was outstanding.

	I hope it makes better appeals
	next time, though."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_GotNervous {
	"Spectator: When the {STR_VAR_2} got
	nervous, I couldn't stop myself from
	shouting encouragement.

	I'd like to say this to that
	{STR_VAR_2}, “Congratulations!”"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_StartledFoes {
	"Spectator: That {STR_VAR_2}'s appeal
	startled even me!

	{STR_VAR_2}, you were awesome!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_UsedCombo {
	"Spectator: That {STR_VAR_2}'s combo
	appeal was stunning!

	It's shaken me to the core!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_ExcitingAppeal {
	"Spectator: The winning {STR_VAR_2}'s
	appeal got my heart pounding!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_WasCool {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You were cool!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_WasBeautiful {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You were beautiful!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_WasCute {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You were cute!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_WasSmart {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You were smart!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_WasTough {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You were tough!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_VeryExcitingAppeal {
	"Spectator: The winning {STR_VAR_2}'s
	appeal still has my heart pounding!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_VeryCool {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You're the last word in cool!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_VeryBeautiful {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You're the most beautiful!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_VeryCute {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You're simply the cutest!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_VerySmart {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You're the smartest among the smart!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_VeryTough {
	"{STR_VAR_2}!
	You're the toughest of the tough!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_TookBreak {
	"Spectator: Even when the {STR_VAR_2}
	took a break from making appeals,
	I couldn't take my eyes off it.

	I'm captivated by that {STR_VAR_2}."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_GotStartled {
	"Spectator: When the {STR_VAR_2} was
	startled by another POKéMON's appeal,
	I was close to tears.

	{STR_VAR_2}, you were resilient!
	Way to go!"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_MoveWonderful {
	"Spectator: Oh…
	That {STR_VAR_2}'s {STR_VAR_3}!
	{STR_VAR_2}'s {STR_VAR_3}!
	{STR_VAR_2}'s {STR_VAR_3}!
	How could it be so wonderful?"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_TalkAboutAnotherMon {
	"MC: Well, there you have it. This place
	is full of the {STR_VAR_1}'s fans!

	I should also mention that another
	POKéMON, {STR_VAR_2}'s {STR_VAR_3}, 
	caught my eye.

	{STR_VAR_2}'s {STR_VAR_3}…"
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_FailedToAppeal {
	"It failed to make a single appeal during
	secondary judging out of nervousness.

	Next time, I would like to see this
	{STR_VAR_1} make even one appeal."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_LastInBothRounds {
	"It came dead last in both primary
	and secondary judging.

	I hope that {STR_VAR_1} will retrain this
	{STR_VAR_2} and erase the shame of
	this undisputed last-place finish."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_NotExcitingEnough {
	"It failed to take advantage of
	the audience's excitement and make
	an appropriate appeal.

	We hope {STR_VAR_1} will learn how to get
	a feel for the audience and whip their
	excitement to a fever pitch next time."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_LostAfterWinningRound1 {
	"While finishing first in the primary
	judging, its appeals in the secondary
	judging failed to click.

	It suffered a humiliating come-from-
	behind loss.

	I'm sure {STR_VAR_1} is studying how to
	make more effective appeals now."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_NeverExciting {
	"The audience never got excited by its
	appeals during the secondary judging.

	We hope it will stop worrying about
	other POKéMON and learn to pitch
	its appeals to the audience more."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_LostBySmallMargin {
	"It lost to {STR_VAR_1}'s {STR_VAR_2}
	by only a small margin.

	It must be heartbreaking to come
	so close to victory only to fail.

	I wouldn't be surprised if {STR_VAR_3}
	were weeping over this outcome."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_RepeatedAppeals {
	"It disappointed the JUDGE by
	repeating the same appeals.

	It's an unforgivable error in any
	CONTEST, and the POKéMON paid.

	{STR_VAR_1} should feel guilty for
	this sorry showing."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_ValiantEffortButLost {
	"{STR_VAR_1} turned in a valiant effort,
	but…

	It was all for naught, finishing last.

	{STR_VAR_1} should learn from this loss
	and put the knowledge to good use."
}

text ContestLiveUpdates_Text_Outro {
	"I'd like to end this program with our
	usual farewell to the winners.

	This time, it's {STR_VAR_1} and
	the {STR_VAR_2}!

	MC: Is everyone ready?
	All together now!

	Audience: {STR_VAR_1}! {STR_VAR_2}!
	Congratulations!
	You're the CONTEST winner!"
}

text gTVPokemonBattleUpdateText00 {
	"“POKéMON BATTLE UPDATE!”

	Bringing you the results of POKéMON
	battles as they come in!"
}

text gTVPokemonBattleUpdateText01 {
	"The TRAINERS {STR_VAR_1} and
	{STR_VAR_2} faced each other in
	a {STR_VAR_3} BATTLE.

	This match ended in victory for
	{STR_VAR_1}!"
}

text gTVPokemonBattleUpdateText02 {
	"In the battle, {STR_VAR_1}'s
	{STR_VAR_2} was a formidable force
	using {STR_VAR_3}!"
}

text gTVPokemonBattleUpdateText03 {
	"{STR_VAR_1}'s {STR_VAR_2} had a weak
	showing that really hurt."
}

text gTVPokemonBattleUpdateText04 {
	"Congratulations on your victory,
	{STR_VAR_1}!

	And for the defeated {STR_VAR_2},
	we hope for a better result next time!

	This concludes this episode of
	“POKéMON BATTLE UPDATE!”"
}

text gTVPokemonBattleUpdateText05 {
	"The teams of TRAINERS {STR_VAR_1} and
	{STR_VAR_2} met in a MULTI BATTLE.

	This match ended in victory for
	{STR_VAR_1}'s team."
}

text gTVPokemonBattleUpdateText06 {
	"In the battle, the {STR_VAR_2} on
	{STR_VAR_1}'s team was a formidable
	force using {STR_VAR_3}."
}

text gTVPokemonBattleUpdateText07 {
	"The weak showing by the {STR_VAR_3}
	on {STR_VAR_2}'s team really hurt.

	Congratulations on your team's
	victory, {STR_VAR_1}!

	As for the defeated {STR_VAR_2}'s team,
	we hope for a better result next time!

	This concludes this episode of
	“POKéMON BATTLE UPDATE!”"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_GabbyPreFirstBattle {
	"GABBY: Oh! We've just spotted a tough-
	looking TRAINER here of all places!

	Okay, roll camera!
	Let's get this interview."
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_GabbyIntro {
	"GABBY: Oh! You're {PLAYER}! Hi!
	Do you remember us from last time?

	Can you show us how much stronger
	you've become? Okay, cue interview!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_GabbyDefeatFirstTime {
	"GABBY: My eyes didn't lie!
	I did discover an astonishing TRAINER!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_WhoAreYouInterview {
	"GABBY: Awesome! Awesome!
	Who are you?!

	I knew we were onto something wild
	when we spotted you!

	Oh, please let me explain. We travel
	around everywhere interviewing all
	sorts of TRAINERS.

	So, would you give us a bit of your time
	for an interview?"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_QuoteFromLastInterview {
	"GABBY: “{STR_VAR_1}!”

	Remember? That's the quote you gave
	us as the battle clincher last time.

	I never, ever forget stuff like that!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_YouStompedUsInterviewAgain {
	"The last time we battled, you stomped
	us before we could brace ourselves…

	Anyway, what do you think?
	Do you want to be interviewed again?"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_YouThrewABallAtUsInterviewAgain {
	"The last time we battled, didn't you
	throw a POKé BALL at us?

	We were shocked! So we told everyone,
	just everyone, about it!

	Anyway, what do you think?
	Do you want to be interviewed again?"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_CleverItemSkillsInterviewAgain {
	"The last time we battled, your item
	skills cleverly did us in.

	Anyway, what do you think?
	Do you want to be interviewed again?"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_WeLookedRespectableInterviewAgain {
	"The last time we battled, we managed
	to look respectable.

	Anyway, what do you think?
	Do you want to be interviewed again?"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_InterviewAgain {
	"Anyway, what do you think?
	Do you want to be interviewed again?"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_DescribeYourFeelings {
	"You will?
	Thank you!

	Okay, I need you to describe your
	feelings about our battle, but it
	has to be short and sweet. Go!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_PerfectWellBeSeeingYou {
	"GABBY: Mmm, yeah!
	That's the perfect clincher!

	I get the feeling that this will make
	a great TV show.

	There's a chance that they'll air this
	on TV, so make sure to look for us!

	Okay!
	We'll be seeing you!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_DontGiveUpKeepingEyeOut {
	"GABBY: Oh…

	Okay, but don't give up!
	We'll be keeping an eye out for you!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_KeepingAnEyeOutForYou {
	"GABBY: We'll be keeping an eye out
	for you!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_GabbyNotEnoughMons {
	"GABBY: Is there a strong TRAINER
	anywhere with a lot of POKéMON?"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_GiveUsAnInterviewThisTime {
	"GABBY: Wow, you are something!

	You've gotten a lot stronger--a lot--
	since we last battled.

	We were right about you when we
	spotted you as a hot TRAINER.

	So, anyway, what do you think?
	Are you willing to give us an interview
	this time?"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_GabbyDefeat {
	"GABBY: That was an intense battle!
	Did you get all that on camera?"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_TyPreFirstBattle {
	"TY: Hey, lookie here! A tough-looking
	TRAINER here, of all places!
	Camera's rolling!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_TyIntro {
	"TY: Hey, lookie here!
	I remember you!

	I'll get this battle all on this
	here camera!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_TyPostBattle {
	"TY: You're a natural!
	Got me some prime footage right here!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_TyNotEnoughMons {
	"TY: Do you only have the one POKéMON
	and that's it?

	If you had more POKéMON, it'd make for
	better footage, but…"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_TyDefeatFirstTime {
	"TY: Yep, we sure spotted a hot TRAINER.
	This is a huge scoop for us!"
}

text GabbyAndTy_Text_TyDefeat {
	"TY: Yep, I got it all.
	That whole battle's on camera."
}

text gTVInSearchOfTrainersText00 {
	"IN SEARCH OF TRAINERS…

	GABBY: Hi! Today I'm visiting an area
	near {STR_VAR_1}.

	We're trying to spot some up-and-
	coming new talent in the field.

	Today, we turned our lens on the
	TRAINER {PLAYER}.

	There's something about this TRAINER
	that piqued our interest."
}

text gTVInSearchOfTrainersText01 {
	"We've battled {PLAYER} before, but we
	can attest that the TRAINER has most
	definitely improved from before.

	I knew we were onto someone special
	when we spotted this TRAINER!"
}

text gTVInSearchOfTrainersText02 {
	"The best way to determine how strong
	a TRAINER is…

	Well, the fastest way is to battle.
	And so we began our investigation!

	… …

	That's how we ended up in battle
	with {PLAYER}.

	In a dominating performance, we were
	flattened, rolled up, and tossed aside!

	{PLAYER} is ruthlessly strong…

	Here's our impressions after having
	battled our featured TRAINER."
}

text gTVInSearchOfTrainersText03 {
	"The combination of {STR_VAR_1} and
	{STR_VAR_3} was divine!

	The sight of them--{STR_VAR_1} and
	{STR_VAR_3}--selflessly supporting
	each other in the thick of battle…

	It was a marvelous sight to behold!

	{STR_VAR_2} was the move the TRAINER
	used last in our battle.

	The move {STR_VAR_2} is {STR_VAR_1}
	and {STR_VAR_3}'s sign of friendship!"
}

text gTVInSearchOfTrainersText04 {
	"…I lost confidence in myself as
	a result of our encounter.

	We were beaten before we could launch
	a single attack.
	Ohhh… Snivel…

	In spite of that, {PLAYER}'s battles
	are worth seeing.

	I recommend confident TRAINERS to
	challenge {PLAYER}."
}

text gTVInSearchOfTrainersText05 {
	"There's only one thing to be said.
	Don't you dare throw a POKé BALL during
	a TRAINER battle!

	{PLAYER} is certainly strong, but has
	no clue about the basic rules.

	To our TV audience, I have a request.

	If you see {PLAYER}, please caution
	the TRAINER!"
}

text gTVInSearchOfTrainersText06 {
	"{PLAYER} is adept at reading the
	opponent's actions.

	The timing of item usage was remarkably
	effective!"
}

text gTVInSearchOfTrainersText07 {
	"Honestly speaking, I thought that
	I might even be pretty good.

	While we did end up losing, we did have
	a hotly contested battle.

	But if you're struggling against me,
	you have a ways to go, {PLAYER}!"
}

text gTVInSearchOfTrainersText08 {
	"After our battle, we asked {PLAYER} for
	a succinct summary.

	The TRAINER replied, “{STR_VAR_1}.”

	{PLAYER}'s POKéMON {STR_VAR_2} and
	{STR_VAR_3}…
	And “{STR_VAR_1}”…

	Mmm! That's deep! There's deep
	significance behind that quote!

	It's no surprise--a good TRAINER has
	good things to say.

	That's all for today!
	See you again on our next broadcast!"
}

text ContestLadyShow_Text_Intro {
	"“POKéMON CONTEST LIVE UPDATES!”

	MC: Sorry to interrupt the regular
	programming, and thanks for joining us!

	We bring you this live from
	the scene of a just-completed
	{STR_VAR_1}!

	Spectators: ?!!!!

	MC: Oh! It looks like the CONTEST
	participants are headed this way!

	I'll try to get an impromptu interview
	for you folks at home!

	Spectators: ?!!!!
	?!!!!"
}

text ContestLadyShow_Text_Won {
	"MC: Excuse me!
	Thanks for joining us on live TV!

	May I congratulate you on your win?

	What was the key factor in today's
	stunning victory?

	BEAUTY: We gave it our best effort
	today, my {STR_VAR_2} and I!

	But I'm sure we wouldn't have made it
	if it weren't for all the help we
	received leading up to the CONTEST!

	MC: Do you have a special someone
	with whom you'd like to share your joy?
	Let's hear it live!

	BEAUTY: Hey, out there!

	{STR_VAR_3}! Are you watching?
	We did it!
	Thank you!"
}

text ContestLadyShow_Text_Lost {
	"MC: Excuse me!
	Thanks for joining us on live TV!

	You must be disappointed by that turn
	of events. Do you have any comments?

	BEAUTY: It's heartbreaking…
	My {STR_VAR_2} and I, we did our best…

	But I feel like I've let down everyone
	who has supported us through this.

	MC: I hate to say it, but the POKéMON's
	coloration is a little wanting.

	BEAUTY: {STR_VAR_3}, I'm so sorry…
	I'll do better next time, I swear…
	…Sniff… Waaaaah!

	Spectators: See that?
	The poor girl!

	MC: Uh… Uh-oh…

	Uh… That's all the time we have today!
	Thanks for tuning in!"
}

text ContestLadyShow_Text_LostBadly {
	"MC: Excuse me!
	Thanks for joining us on live TV!

	How did your CONTEST appearance go?

	BEAUTY: Nothing went right…
	For some reason, my {STR_VAR_2}
	couldn't attract any popularity.

	MC: I hate to say it, but the POKéMON's
	coloration is a little wanting.

	BEAUTY: … … … … … …
	…Sniff… Waaaaah!

	Spectators: See that?
	The poor girl!

	MC: Uh… Uh-oh…

	Uh… That's all the time we have today!
	Thanks for tuning in!"
}
